      • searchTermByName

        Set<OntologyTermI> searchTermByName(String name)
        Search for terms using a preferred name or synonym. The search is case insensitive. It iterates through all loaded ontologies, so use with caution!
        Parameters:
        name - - term name (not ID)
        Returns:

      • searchTermByName

        Set<OntologyTermI> searchTermByName(String name,
                                    Set<String> ontologies)
        Search for terms by name or synonym. The search is case insensitive. It still iterates over all available ontologies, but skips ones other than specified in the second parameter.
        Parameters:
        name - - term name (not ID)
        ontologies - to look into
